{
  "stem": "22979.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And some of those twins survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I just heard them on the television talking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And well, all kinds of inhuman things what went on there, which, you know, I don't even recall at [? the ?] [? spur of the ?] moment because I have so much what I saw.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I can hardly come to-- even I will talk to you, you know, days and days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, one Czech, very famous poet what I mentioned, which I [? gave ?] the book.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was published in 1946 in the publishing company where I was an employee.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the motto, you know, the first page of the-- it was picture book of children who were also killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the title of the book was, You see the whole book.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's-- it's a beautiful-- I mean, a beautiful-- well done photographs, which I don't know where they found them-- children from all over Europe-- from Yugoslavia, from the Ukraine-- because they didn't [? got ?] to Russia.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were only in the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "From everywhere.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "From the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Czechoslovakia, a publishing company, [NON-ENGLISH], where I was working for 15 years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was only published, I think so, 3,000.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- when we came here, I brought the book.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later when the Holocaust library was formed, I gave them about 10, 15 books, all from camp because the company where I was working published all those books.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got them right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- and there was a letter from a little Polish boy from a ghetto who said-- just what I recall.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He writes a letter to his parents because he was caught somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I am here in this miserable place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have no shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm hungry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My clothes-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] my clothes are torn.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
